{"tid":904753,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"如果柒頭屈機男2015年買左樓，今日日子會如何？","createTime":"2018-11-16T15:12:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T02:57:07.000Z","uid":103921,"like":21,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7b9957d882a3dec45810343caa5d99fee80c2a27","tid":904753,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:12:55.000Z","msg":"2015年柒頭屈機男已經唱淡樓市股市，引來一眾盲毛追隨。之後股樓皆升，信徒都反晒枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屈狗為挽回劣勢，多次撩人隻揪，甚至自稱擁12M物業，但最終又係敗走收場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果屈狗2015年肯聽話買左嘉湖而唔係笑林太，今日日子會如何？ (當然可能佢根本30萬都比唔出，純粹得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k9r15Z0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk9r15Z0.jpg&h=db49bd85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad0f95e52c5356fc13d2684e247a72fd58cecdaa","tid":904753,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:14:44.000Z","msg":"屈狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4da9837066b72dd9b4a27c83b0d35b566c71540","tid":904753,"uid":103921,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:15:40.000Z","msg":"如果屈狗一早買左樓，就唔使日日精神病漢咁咀咒業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n十足維園痴線佬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c62c10cede14683f7ef4eea6690d46bfa9002bd","tid":904753,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"屈狗負皮又唔敢回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7ae74c11d7f4478244a472adb95a4706d6733d","tid":904753,"uid":103921,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:28:05.000Z","msg":"計下屈狗有幾多個acc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkg